(147, '放飞梦想，迎接挑战——2012国际商务硕士（DDIM项目）开学系列活动拉开序幕', 'cn', 0, 6, '', '', '<p>\n	<strong></strong>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 近日，2012国际商务硕士（DDIM项目）开学系列活动拉开序幕。该项目是由我校、意大利博科尼大学和意大利路易斯大学共同合作开办的。项目2012级共招收80名学生，其中45名来自意大利，35名为中国学生。开学伊始，为促进师生间的交流和沟通，帮助中意学生更好地融合，也为了让意大利学生更快地适应复旦校园，项目开展了一系列开学培训拓展活动。\n</p>\n<p style="text-align:center;">\n	<img alt="" src="http://www.fdsm.fudan.edu.cn/UserWebEditorUploadImage/J2nlSDxtSEk/20120926011.jpg" height="266" width="500" />　\n</p>\n<p align="center">\n	来自中意两国的80位新生正式加入DDIM项目大家庭\n</p>\n<p>\n	<strong>入学指导，明确方向</strong> \n</p>\n<p>\n	&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 9月6日，项目办公室对DDIM新生进行了入学指导，全面介绍了项目培养方案、课程设置、第二课堂等内容，同时也对学生关心的选课、考试等问题进行了详细说明。在破冰小游戏后，中意学生们进行了积极交流，憧憬着未来两年的学习生活。通过指导会的讲解和与新同学的交流，新生们对项目有了更深的了解，对自己今后的学习也有了更为具体明确的目标和方向。\n</p>\n<p>\n	<strong>开学典礼，整装待发</strong> \n</p>\n<p>\n	9月13日，中意两国新生齐聚一堂，共同参加项目的开学典礼，由此正式拉开了新学期的序幕。意大利总领事馆Vincenzo De Luca 先生、博科尼大学DDIM项目学术主任Markus Venzin教授、路易斯大学工商管理学院院长Gennaro Olivieri教授、我院殷志文副院长、意方两所大学大学上海地区校友会代表等参加了本次典礼。中意双方代表共同祝愿，同学们在今后的两年学习生活中充分体验中意文化交融的乐趣，并在课堂内外的学习中有所收获。\n</p>\n<p style="text-align:center;">\n	　<img alt="" src="http://www.fdsm.fudan.edu.cn/UserWebEditorUploadImage/J2nlSDxtSEk/20120926012.jpg" height="550" width="496" /> \n</p>\n<p align="center">\n	中意两国学生在交流与合作中结下友谊\n</p>\n<p>\n	<strong>户外拓展，熔炼团队</strong> \n</p>\n<p>\n	&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 9月21日，项目团队带领新生们来到东方绿舟进行了为期一天的户外拓展活动。同学之间开展了丰富多样的互动游戏，结成小组进行了紧张激烈的龙舟比赛，展开了考验体力与耐力的铁人三项比拼等等。一天的拓展活动不但展示了新生们个人的魅力和风采，增进了同学之间的友谊，更让大家在游戏中体会到团队合作的重要性。最终，项目还评出了最具合作精神团队、最具创意团队和最佳表现团队，并颁发了纪念奖品。\n</p>\n<p>\n	&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 在开学系列活动之后，迎接各位新同学的将是紧张的学习生活，期待新同学们能通过两年不断的努力和奋斗，交出一份让老师、家长以及自己满意的答卷，向着成为国际化管理型人才的目标迈出坚实的一步！　\n</p>', '', '', '', '', '/201210/26/103526tz9yjz4lpqggzsn8.jpg', ' 近日，2012国际商务硕士（DDIM项目）开学系列活动拉开序幕。该项目是由我校、意大利博科尼大学和意大利路易斯大学共同合作开办的。项目2012级共招收80名学生，其中45名来自意大利，35名为中国学生。开学伊始，为促进师生间的交流和沟通，帮助中意学生更好地融合，也为了让意大利学生更快地适应复旦校园，项目开展了一系列开学培训拓展活动。', 1351136073, 0, 1, '', 4, '2012-10-01 ', 'Open Up Your Dreams and Meet Challenges –DDIM 2012 Class Opening Series Activities Kick', 'Recently, DDIM 2012 Class Opening Series Activities kicked off. This programme was jointly launched by Fudan University, Bocconi University and Luiss University of Italy. 2012 Class of this program admitted 80 students, in whom 45 are from Italy and 35 from China. At the beginning of this new term, in order to promote the exchange and communication between teachers and students, to help better integrate Chinese students with Italian students and to assist Italian students in adapting to the camp', '<div id="trans-result-content" lang="EN-US">\n	<p>\n		<span class="">\n		<p style="margin-left:0cm;text-indent:24.0pt;background:white;">\n			<span style="font-size:9.0pt;font-family:&quot;color:#3B3B3B;">Recently, DDIM 2012 Class Opening Series Activities kicked off.\nThis programme was jointly launched by Fudan University, Bocconi University and\nLuiss University of Italy. 2012 Class of this program admitted 80 students, in\nwhom 45 are from Italy and 35 from China. At the beginning of this new term, in\norder to promote the exchange and communication between teachers and students,\nto help better integrate Chinese students with Italian students and to assist\nItalian students in adapting to the campus of Fudan University more quickly,\nthis program has been carried out with some term opening training and extension\nactivities.</span><span style="font-size:9.0pt;font-family:&quot;color:#3B3B3B;"></span>\n		</p>\n</span><span class=""></span> \n	</p>\n</div>\n<p align="center">\n	<img alt="" src="http://www.fdsm.fudan.edu.cn/UserWebEditorUploadImage/J2nlSDxtSEk/20120926011.jpg" height="266" width="500" />　\n</p>\n<p align="center">\n	<p style="margin-left:0cm;text-align:center;text-indent:24.0pt;background:white;" align="center">\n		<span style="font-size:9.0pt;font-family:&quot;color:#3B3B3B;">Eighty new students from China and Italy formally joining the\nbig family of DDIM program</span><span style="font-size:9.0pt;font-family:&quot;color:#3B3B3B;"></span>\n	</p>\n	<p style="margin-left:0cm;text-align:center;text-indent:24.0pt;background:white;" align="center">\n		<p style="margin-left:0cm;text-align:left;text-indent:24.0pt;background:white;" align="left">\n			<span><span style="font-size:9.0pt;font-family:&quot;color:#3B3B3B;"><strong>Orientation\npointing out definitive directions</strong></span></span><span style="font-size:9.0pt;font-family:&quot;color:#3B3B3B;"></span>\n		</p>\n<br />\n<span style="font-size:9.0pt;font-family:&quot;color:#3B3B3B;"></span>\n	</p>\n<span class=""></span> \n</p>\n<p>\n	<span class="">\n	<p style="margin-left:0cm;text-indent:24.0pt;background:white;">\n		<span style="font-size:9.0pt;font-family:&quot;color:#3B3B3B;">On September 6, the program office provided orientation to new\nstudents of DDIM, introducing the programme training plan, curriculum and the\nsecond classroom etc., across the board and detailing the course selection and\nexam and other questions, which students are concerned about. After some\nicebreaking games, these students of China and Italy actively communicated with\neach other and looked forward to the study and life in the next two years.\nThrough the presentation of the guidance meeting and exchange with new\nclassmates, the new students had better understanding of this programme, and\nalso had more specific objectives and directions of their future study.</span>\n	</p>\n</span><span class=""></span> \n</p>\n<div id="trans-result-content" lang="EN-US">\n	<p>\n		<span>\n		<p style="margin-left:0cm;text-indent:24.0pt;background:white;">\n			<span><span style="font-size:9.0pt;font-family:&quot;color:#3B3B3B;"><strong>Attending\nthe Semester Opening Ceremony to be fully prepared for the future</strong></span></span><span style="font-size:9.0pt;font-family:&quot;color:#3B3B3B;"></span>\n		</p>\n<br />\n</span> \n	</p>\n	<p>\n		<span>I\n		<p style="margin-left:0cm;text-indent:24.0pt;background:white;">\n			<span style="font-size:9.0pt;font-family:&quot;color:#3B3B3B;">On September 13, the new Chinese and Italian students gathered\ntogether and attended the semester opening ceremony of this programme, thus\nmarking the beginning of this new semester. Mr. Vincenzo De Luca, Consulate\nGeneral of Italy, Professor Markus Venzin, Academic Director of DDIM programme\nof Bocconi University, Professor Gennaro Olivieri, Dean of College of Business\nAdministration of Luiss University, Yin Zhiwen, Associate Dean of FDSM, and\nrepresentatives of the alumni associations of the two Italian universities in\nShanghai, etc., took part in this ceremony. The representatives of China and\nItaly sides jointly wished that the students would fully experience the\npleasure of cultural blending of China and Italy and benefit from the study in\nand out of classroom.</span><span style="font-size:9.0pt;font-family:&quot;color:#3B3B3B;"></span>\n		</p>\n</span><span class=""></span> \n	</p>\n</div>\n<p>\n	<br />\n</p>\n<p>\n	<br />\n</p>\n<p style="text-align:center;">\n	　<img alt="" src="http://www.fdsm.fudan.edu.cn/UserWebEditorUploadImage/J2nlSDxtSEk/20120926012.jpg" height="550" width="496" />\n</p>\n<p style="text-align:center;">\n	<p style="margin-left:0cm;text-align:center;text-indent:24.0pt;background:white;" align="center">\n		<span style="font-size:9.0pt;font-family:&quot;color:#3B3B3B;">The students from China and Italy forge a friendship in the\nexchange and cooperation.</span><span style="font-size:9.0pt;font-family:&quot;color:#3B3B3B;"></span>\n	</p>\n	<p style="margin-left:0cm;text-align:left;text-indent:24.0pt;background:white;" align="left">\n		<span style="font-size:9.0pt;font-family:&quot;color:#3B3B3B;"><strong>Outdoor extension aiming to forge the team</strong></span><span style="font-size:9.0pt;font-family:&quot;color:#3B3B3B;"></span>\n	</p>\n</p>\n<div id="trans-result-content" lang="EN-US">\n	<p>\n		<span class=""></span><span class=""></span><span class=""></span><span class=""></span> \n	</p>\n</div>\n<p>\n	<br />\n</p>\n<p>\n	<strong> </strong>\n</p>\n<div id="trans-result-content" lang="EN-US">\n	<p>\n		<span class="">\n		<p style="margin-left:0cm;text-indent:24.0pt;background:white;">\n			<span style="font-size:9.0pt;font-family:&quot;color:#3B3B3B;">On September 21, the programme team led new students to Oriental\nLand to conduct one-day outdoor extension activities. They played a great\nvariety of interactive games, held intense, fierce dragon boat races in the\nform of groups, and participated in the triathlon competition to test physical\nstrength and endurance, and so on. The one-day extension activities not only\nshowed the personal charm of these new students, enhanced the friendship\nbetween them, but also offered as an opportunity for them to experience the\nimportance of teamwork in games. At the end, the programme also selected the\nmost cooperative team, the most creative team and the best performed team, and\nawarded them souvenirs.</span>\n		</p>\n		<p style="margin-left:0cm;text-indent:24.0pt;background:white;">\n			<span style="font-size:9.0pt;font-family:&quot;color:#3B3B3B;">\n			<p style="margin-left:0cm;text-indent:24.0pt;background:white;">\n				<span style="font-size:9.0pt;font-family:&quot;color:#3B3B3B;">After the opening series activities, these new students will\nface intense school life. We hope that after two years of efforts they will be\nable to achieve good results satisfactory to their teachers, parents and\nthemselves, and thus make a solid step towards the objective of being\ninternational management talents!</span><span style="font-size:9.0pt;font-family:&quot;color:#3B3B3B;"></span>\n			</p>\n			<p style="margin-left:0cm;text-indent:24.0pt;background:white;">\n				<span style="font-size:9.0pt;font-family:&quot;color:#3B3B3B;"></span>\n			</p>\n<br />\n</span>\n		</p>\n</span>\n	</p>\n</div>\n<br />'),
(60, '国际商务硕士项目常见问题', 'cn', 0, 13, '', '', '<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<strong>Q：国际商务硕士项目的学费多少，有无奖学金？</strong><br />\r\nA：2013年免收学费，可享受复旦大学研究生奖学金。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<strong>Q：国际商务硕士学习方式是怎么样的，可以在职学习吗？</strong><br />\r\nA：国际商务硕士均为全日制脱产学习。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<strong>Q：参加考研的话，国际商务硕士的考试科目是什么？</strong><br />\r\n<span style="color:#000000;">A：</span><span style="font-size:9pt;color:#000000;font-family:‘Verdana‘,‘sans-serif‘;">2013</span><span style="font-size:9pt;color:#000000;font-family:宋体;">年考试科目为</span><span style="font-size:9pt;color:#000000;font-family:‘Verdana‘,‘sans-serif‘;">101</span><span style="font-size:9pt;color:#000000;font-family:宋体;">思想政治理论、</span><span style="font-size:9pt;color:#000000;font-family:‘Verdana‘,‘sans-serif‘;">201</span><span style="font-size:9pt;color:#000000;font-family:宋体;">英语一、</span><span style="font-size:9pt;color:#000000;font-family:‘Verdana‘,‘sans-serif‘;">303</span><span style="font-size:9pt;color:#000000;font-family:宋体;">数学三和</span><span style="font-size:9pt;color:#000000;font-family:‘Verdana‘,‘sans-serif‘;">434</span><span style="font-size:9pt;color:#000000;font-family:宋体;">国际商务专业基础。具体信息请登陆</span><span style="font-size:9pt;color:#000000;font-family:‘Verdana‘,‘sans-serif‘;"> <span style="color:#000000;">http://www.urp.fudan.edu.cn:79/jzfb/main.jsp?siteId=3&amp;pageId=17&amp;zslbdm=11 </span></span><span style="font-size:9pt;color:#000000;font-family:宋体;">查阅</span><span style="font-size:9pt;color:#000000;font-family:‘Verdana‘,‘sans-serif‘;">2013</span><span style="font-size:9pt;color:#000000;font-family:宋体;">年招生专业目录。</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<strong>Q：管理学院有哪些项目招生？ </strong><br />\r\nA：近年来管理学院的硕士研究生招生实行改革： <br />\r\n1、从2008年起应用经济学、管理科学与工程、工商管理下设各专业按一级学科统一招生，实行硕博连读。概率论与数理统计、运筹学与控制论自2011年起实行硕博连读。 <br />\r\n2、企业管理—中意双硕士学位项目（DDIM）自2011年起转为国际商务（025400）硕士专业学位招生，本项目不收学费，培养方式同历年做法。<br />\r\n3、财务管理（120222）和金融工程管理（120223）即金融硕士项目，学制两年。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<strong>Q：管理学院招生方式有哪些？ </strong><br />\r\nA：目前的硕士招生方式有推免和公开招考，每年会通过夏令营活动预录取部分推免名额，10月统一招收推免生（含外校和本校）。博士招生方式有硕博连读学生直接转博和公开招考两种方式。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<strong>Q：如何报名？ </strong><br />\r\nA：推免生和公开招考生分别通过以下方式报名： <br />\r\n1、推免生：请考生分清是要攻读我院的硕士项目（国际商务、财务管理、金融工程管理）还是硕博连读项目（应用经济学、管理科学与工程、工商管理三个一级学科，概率论与数理统计、运筹学与控制论两个专业），通过我校研究生招生网 www.gsao.fudan.edu.cn 报名，并在网上报名时正确填写所报考的院系、学科（专业）、研究方向、考试科目及其对应的代码。 <br />\r\n2、公开招考生：请关注我校研究生招生网 www.gsao.fudan.edu.cn 相关通知。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<strong>Q：是否接收外校推免生？如何申请？ </strong><br />\r\nA：我院除了通过夏令营进行外校推免生预录取工作之外，根据学校的相关规定，还将继续接受其他申请人的推免申请，请考生登陆管理学院网站 www.fdsm.fudan.edu.cn “科学学位项目--研究生--招生信息--招生快讯”浏览相关通知并按要求进行网上报名和申请材料递交。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<strong>Q：硕士推免生名额的比例大致为多少？是否按学科或专业分配？ <br />\r\n</strong>A：2013年推免生占总招生计划数的<span style="font-size:9pt;color:#000000;font-family:‘Verdana‘,‘sans-serif‘;">70—80%</span><span style="color:#000000;">，</span>但具体学科、专业会因各自的实际情况而有所不同。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<strong>Q：复试科目有哪些？复试方式及差额复试比例是怎样的？ </strong><br />\r\nA：具体请登陆我校研究生招生网 www.gsao.fudan.edu.cn 查询，差额复试比例一般为1：1.2（生源好的学科专业可以1：1.5比例差额复试）。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<strong>Q：关于拟录取名单是如何确定的？ </strong><br />\r\nA：学院将综合考生的初试成绩（占50%）、复试成绩（占50%，含综合素质打分和复试表现）计算总成绩，按招生计划名额从高到低，择优录取。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<strong>Q：管理学院是否开设考研辅导班？是否出售历年考题、考纲等考研资料？ </strong><br />\r\nA：不开设。我院不提供历年的考研试题和复习资料的出售等服务，请各位考生自行复习。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<strong>Q：是否招生港澳台学生和留学生？ </strong><br />\r\nA：2013年各项目暂不招收港澳台学生和留学生。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<strong>Q：关于2013年研究生入学考试参考书目？ </strong><br />\r\n<span style="color:#000000;">A：</span><span style="font-size:9pt;color:#000000;font-family:宋体;">根据学校精神，</span><span style="font-size:9pt;color:#000000;font-family:‘Verdana‘,‘sans-serif‘;">2013</span><span style="font-size:9pt;color:#000000;font-family:宋体;">年我校研究生入学考试原则上不列参考书目。</span><span style="font-size:9pt;color:#4c4c4c;font-family:‘Verdana‘,‘sans-serif‘;"> </span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>', '', '', '', '', '', '问：硕士推免生名额的比例大致为多少？是否按学科或专业分配?<br>\r\n答：2011年推免生占总招生计划数的60—70%，但具体学科、专业会因各自的实际情况而有所不同。', 1317195190, 0, 1, '', 0, '2012-11-23', 'Master of international business project FAQ', 'Ask: Master pushes exempts lives ended roughly in proportion to the number? Whether the subject or professional distribution? <br>\r\n\r\nAnswer: 2011 pushes exempts lives in total enrollment plan of 60 - 70%, but the specific disciplines, professional due to their actual vary.', '<div lang="EN-US" id="trans-result-content">\r\n	<p>\r\n		<span class="">Q</span><span>:</span><span class=""> Master of international business</span><span> project</span><span> tuition fee number</span><span>,</span><span> there is</span><span> no</span><span class=""> scholarship</span><span>?</span> \r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n		<span class="">A:2012</span><span class=""> years</span><span class=""> free of tuition fees</span><span>,</span><span> can enjoy the</span><span> Fudan University</span><span class=""> graduate scholarship</span><span>.</span> \r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n		<span>Q</span><span>:</span><span class=""> International</span><span class=""> Master of business</span><span> mode of learning is</span><span> like,</span><span> can</span><span> learn on the job</span><span>?</span> \r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n		<span>A</span><span>:</span><span class=""> Master of international business</span><span> are</span><span> full-time full-time learning</span><span>.</span> \r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n		<span>Q</span><span>:</span><span> in</span><span> the</span><span> words</span><span>,</span><span class=""> the master of international business</span><span> of the</span><span> examination subject</span><span> is</span><span> what</span><span>?</span> \r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n		<span>A</span><span>:</span><span> test subjects for</span><span> 101</span><span class=""> ideological and political theory</span><span>,</span><span> English</span><span>,</spa