(121, '复旦大学管理学院国际商务硕士项目介绍', 'cn', 0, 30, '', '', '<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-indent:15.75pt;line-height:150%;mso-char-indent-count:1.5;">\n	<span style="font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;">为了满足未来社会对管理人才日益增长的市场需求，同时促进研究生人才培养与社会需求的有效衔接，复旦大学管理学院立足自身资源优势，依托国际合作关系，将中意合作企业管理（</span><span lang="EN-US">Double Degree in International Business</span><span style="font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;">，简称</span><span lang="EN-US">DDIM</span><span style="font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;">）项目转为国际商务专业学位，自</span><span lang="EN-US">2011</span><span style="font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;">年起按照全日制专业学位硕士要求进行招生和培养管理。</span> \n</p>\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height:150%;">\n	<strong style="mso-bidi-font-weight:normal;"><span style="font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;">中意联手合作，培养管理人才</span></strong> \n</p>\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-indent:15.75pt;line-height:150%;mso-char-indent-count:1.5;">\n	<span style="font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;">中国和意大利教育部签署合同推动，由复旦大学、意大利博科尼大学和意大利路易斯大学共同合作开设的管理学双硕士学位项目，旨在培养具有多元化背景、全球视野和国际竞争力的管理学领域新生力量，使之全方位掌握先进的管理理念、熟练运用当代管理手段，进而成为具有扎实管理理论知识的高级应用型专业人才。</span> \n</p>\n<p align="center">\n	<img alt="" src="/uploads/image/20121019/20121019093345_30239.jpg" height="266" width="400" /> \n</p>\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height:150%;">\n	<strong style="mso-bidi-font-weight:normal;"><span style="font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;">跨国学习经历，开阔全球视野</span></strong> \n</p>\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-indent:15.75pt;line-height:150%;mso-char-indent-count:1.5;">\n	<span style="font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;">本项目充分利用中意两国名校资源，资深教授共同指导。学生第一年在复旦大学管理学院与国际学生共同学习基础课程，第二年前往意大利完成专业课程的修读并完成学位论文写作及答辩。赴意大利学习的一年中，可充分领略异国思维，开拓丰厚人生，学习生活环境与国际环境充分接轨。</span> \n</p>\n<p align="center">\n	<img alt="" src="/uploads/image/20121019/20121019093416_60403.jpg" height="266" width="400" /> \n</p>\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height:150%;">\n	<strong style="mso-bidi-font-weight:normal;"><span style="font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;">丰富课程内容，完整英文授课</span></strong> \n</p>\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-indent:15.75pt;line-height:150%;mso-char-indent-count:1.5;">\n	<span style="font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;">本项目课程旨在为学生构建全方位的管理理论框架，掌握管理学的前沿知识与能力，能在企业运作与管理各领域应用自如。课程内容均采用英文授课。</span> \n</p>\n<p align="center">\n	<img alt="" src="/uploads/image/20121019/20121019093449_18651.jpg" height="266" width="400" /> \n</p>\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height:150%;">\n	<strong style="mso-bidi-font-weight:normal;"><span style="font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;">竞争能力卓越，就业前景开阔</span></strong> \n</p>\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-indent:15.75pt;line-height:150%;mso-char-indent-count:1.5;">\n	<span style="font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;">项目着重培养学生参与企业运作的各项实践能力，学生竞争能力强劲。招生过程中即有企业面试官参与，确保生源符合市场需求。同时项目十分重视对学生的职业发展进行技能指导，历届毕业生就业情况良好，在国内外大型集团、合资公司、研究机构等各行业领先企业任职，从事市场开发、人力资源、财务管理、企业战略等工作。</span> \n</p>\n<p align="center">\n	<img alt="" src="/uploads/image/20121019/20121019093512_81021.jpg" height="299" width="400" /> \n</p>\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height:150%;">\n	<strong style="mso-bidi-font-weight:normal;"><span style="font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;">免除全部学费，高额奖金补助</span></strong> \n</p>\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-indent:15.75pt;line-height:150%;mso-char-indent-count:1.5;">\n	<span style="font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;">为了吸引最为优秀的顶尖人才，本项目的中国学生在两年半学习期间免收学费，同时在意大利学习期间，可获得奖学金用以支付住宿费和基本生活费，其中成绩优异者更可获额外奖学金作为奖励。</span> \n</p>\n<p>\n	<br />\n</p>', '', '', '', '', '/201210/19/092711h8m9geaalh5nccvv.jpg', '', 1350354136, 0, 1, '', 0, 'October 16, 2012', 'Introduction to DDIM Programme of FDSM', 'To meet the growing demand for management talents in the future society, and to promote the effective connection between talent training of postgraduate students and social needs, based on its resource advantages, School of Management, Fudan University (FDSM) relies on the international partnership to transform the Double Degree in International Management (DDIM) into the professional degree in international business, and began the recruitment and cultivation management according to the requirem', '<p>\n	<br />\n</p>\n<p style="text-indent:15.75pt;">\n	<span style="font-family:宋体;"></span> \n</p>\n<div id="trans-result-content" lang="EN-US">\n	<p>\n		<span class="">\n		<p style="margin-left:0cm;text-indent:15.75pt;background:white;">\n			<span style="font-family:&quot;color:#3B3B3B;">To meet the growing\ndemand for management talents in the future society, and to promote the\neffective connection between talent training of postgraduate students and\nsocial needs, based on its resource advantages, School of Management, Fudan\nUniversity (FDSM) relies on the international partnership to transform the\nDouble Degree in International Management (DDIM) into the professional degree\nin international business, and began the recruitment and cultivation management\naccording to the requirements of full-time professional degree master in 2011.</span>\n		</p>\n		<p style="margin-left:0cm;text-indent:15.75pt;background:white;">\n			<br />\n<span style="font-family:&quot;color:#3B3B3B;"></span>\n		</p>\n		<p style="margin-left:0cm;text-indent:15.75pt;background:white;">\n			<span style="font-family:&quot;color:#3B3B3B;">\n			<p style="margin-left:0cm;text-indent:24.0pt;background:white;">\n				<span><span style="font-size:10.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:&quot;color:#3B3B3B;">China and\nItaly join hands to cultivate management talents.</span></span>\n			</p>\n			<p style="margin-left:0cm;text-indent:24.0pt;background:white;">\n				<p style="margin-left:0cm;text-indent:15.75pt;background:white;">\n					<span style="font-family:&quot;color:#3B3B3B;">Pushed by the contract\nentered into and between the Ministries of Education of China and Italy, Fudan\nUniversity, Bocconi University of Italy and Luiss University of Italy jointly\nrun the double master degree programme of management science, which aims to train\na new force with a diversification background, an international vision and\ninternational competitiveness in the management science field, and helps them\ngrasp the advanced management concepts across the board, skillfully use the\ncontemporary management tools, and further become senior, professional talents\nwith solid knowledge of management theory.</span><span style="color:#3B3B3B;"> </span>\n				</p>\n<br />\n<span><span style="font-size:10.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:&quot;color:#3B3B3B;"></span></span><span style="color:#3B3B3B;"></span>\n			</p>\n</span><span style="color:#3B3B3B;"> </span><span style="font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;color:#3B3B3B;"></span>\n		</p>\n</span>\n	</p>\n	<p>\n		<span class=""></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span class=""></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span class=""></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span class=""></span><span></span><span></span><span class=""></span><span class=""></span><span class=""></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span class=""></span><span class=""></span><span class=""></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span class=""></span><span></span><span class=""></span><span></span><span class=""></span><span class=""></span> \n	</p>\n</div>\n<p>\n	<br />\n</p>\n<p style="text-indent:15.75pt;">\n	<span style="font-family:宋体;"></span> \n</p>\n<p align="center">\n	<img alt="" src="http://ddim.seabig.cn/uploads/image/20121019/20121019093345_30239.jpg" height="266" width="400" /> \n</p>\n<p>\n	<span class=""><br />\n</span> \n</p>\n<p>\n	<span class="">\n	<p style="margin-left:0cm;text-align:left;text-indent:24.0pt;background:white;" align="left">\n		<span><span style="font-size:10.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:&quot;color:#3B3B3B;">Transnational\nstudy experience helps broaden a global vision</span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;color:#3B3B3B;"></span>\n	</p>\n</span><span class=""></span> \n</p>\n<p align="center">\n	<br />\n</p>\n<div id="trans-result-content" lang="EN-US">\n	<p>\n		<span class="">\n		<p style="margin-left:0cm;text-indent:15.75pt;background:white;">\n			<span style="font-family:&quot;color:#3B3B3B;">This programme makes the\nbest of resources of the well-known universities of China and Italy and has\nsenior professors jointly instruct teaching. In the first year, local students\nwill study basic courses with international students in FDSM; in the second\nyear they will go to Italy to complete the study of major courses, as well as\nthe writing and defense of degree theses there. During the one-year study in\nItaly, students may fully experience exotic thinking, open up a rich life, and\nallow their learning and living environment to fully adapt to international\nenvironment.</span><span style="color:#3B3B3B;"></span>\n		</p>\n</span><span class="highlight"></span> \n	</p>\n</div>\n<p>\n	<br />\n</p>\n<p align="center">\n	<img alt="" src="http://ddim.seabig.cn/uploads/image/20121019/20121019093416_60403.jpg" height="266" width="400" /> \n</p>\n<div id="trans-result-content" lang="EN-US">\n	<p>\n		<span class="">\n		<p style="margin-left:0cm;text-align:left;text-indent:24.0pt;background:white;" align="left">\n			<span><span style="font-size:10.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:&quot;color:#3B3B3B;">Rich course\ncontents given in English</span></span>\n		</p>\n		<p style="margin-left:0cm;text-align:left;text-indent:24.0pt;background:white;" align="left">\n			<p style="margin-left:0cm;text-indent:15.75pt;background:white;">\n				<span style="font-family:&quot;color:#3B3B3B;">The programme course aims\nto build the all-round management theory framework for students, to help them\ngrasp the cutting-edge knowledge and ability of management science, and to\nenable them to freely use such knowledge and ability in the field of corporate\noperation and management. All the courses are given in English.</span><span style="color:#3B3B3B;"></span>\n			</p>\n<br />\n<span><span style="font-size:10.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:&quot;color:#3B3B3B;"></span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;color:#3B3B3B;"></span>\n		</p>\n</span>\n	</p>\n	<p>\n		<span class=""></span><span></span><span class=""></span><span></span><span class=""></span><span class="highlight"></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span class=""></span><span class=""></span><span class=""></span><span></span><span class=""></span><span></span><span></span><span class=""></span><span class=""></span><span class=""></span><span class=""></span> \n	</p>\n</div>\n<br />\n<p align="center">\n	<img alt="" src="http://ddim.seabig.cn/uploads/image/20121019/20121019093449_18651.jpg" height="266" width="400" /> \n</p>\n<div id="trans-result-content" lang="EN-US">\n	<p>\n		<span class="">\n		<p style="margin-left:0cm;text-align:left;text-indent:24.0pt;background:white;" align="left">\n			<span><span style="font-size:10.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:&quot;color:#3B3B3B;">Outstanding\ncompetitiveness with broad career prospects</span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;color:#3B3B3B;"></span>\n		</p>\n</span><span></span> \n	</p>\n	<p>\n		<span class="">\n		<p style="margin-left:0cm;text-indent:15.75pt;background:white;">\n			<span style="font-family:&quot;color:#3B3B3B;">This programme focuses on\ndeveloping students’ practical abilities to participate in corporate operations\nand builds their strong competitiveness. Some interviewers from enterprises\nwill take part in the recruitment to ensure that the student resources meet\nmarket requirements. Meanwhile, with emphasis on the skill guidance of career\ndevelopment of students, it has seen its previous graduates be popular in the market.\nThese students have been employed by some industry-leading enterprises at home\nand abroad, such as large groups, joint ventures and research institutes, to\nengage in market development, human resources, finance management and business\nstrategy and etc..</span><span style="color:#3B3B3B;"></span>\n		</p>\n</span><span class=""></span> \n	</p>\n</div>\n<br />\n<p align="center">\n	<img alt="" src="http://ddim.seabig.cn/uploads/image/20121019/20121019093512_81021.jpg" height="299" width="400" /> \n</p>\n<div id="trans-result-content" lang="EN-US">\n	<p>\n		<span class="">\n		<p style="margin-left:0cm;text-align:left;text-indent:24.0pt;background:white;" align="left">\n			<span><span style="font-size:10.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:&quot;color:#3B3B3B;">Exemption of\nall tuition fees with a handsome scholarship as a subsidy</span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;color:#3B3B3B;"></span>\n		</p>\n</span><span></span> \n	</p>\n	<p>\n		<span class="">\n		<p style="margin-left:0cm;text-indent:15.75pt;background:white;">\n			<span style="font-family:&quot;color:#3B3B3B;">To attract top talents,\nthis programme exempts Chinese students from tuition fees during the 2.5 years\nof study. Meanwhile, during their study in Italy, they are offered with a\nscholarship for their lodging fees and basic living expenses. Besides, a\nstudent with excellent exam results will be provided with an additional\nscholarship as a reward.</span><span style="color:#3B3B3B;"></span>\n		</p>\n</span>\n	</p>\n</div>\n<p>\n	<br />\n</p>\n<br />'),
(142, '管理学院2013年度硕士招生专业目录', 'cn', 0, 12, '', '', '<p style="text-align:center;">\n	<a href="http://msc.fdsm.fudan.edu.cn/uploads/201209/11/0917300kyedb0aavsofltz.jpg" target="_blank"><img alt="" src="http://msc.fdsm.fudan.edu.cn/uploads/201209/11/0917300kyedb0aavsofltz.jpg.thumb.jpg" height="1172" width="500" /></a> \n</p>', '', '', '', '', '', '管理学院2013年度硕士招生专业目录', 1351132904, 0, 1, '', 0, '', 'School of management 2013 year master enrolling new students catalogue of specialty', '', '<p style="text-align:center;">\n	<a href="http://msc.fdsm.fudan.edu.cn/uploads/201209/11/0917300kyedb0aavsofltz.jpg" target="_blank"><img alt="" src="http://msc.fdsm.fudan.edu.cn/uploads/201209/11/0917300kyedb0aavsofltz.jpg.thumb.jpg" height="1172" width="500" /></a> \n</p>\n<br />'),
(144, '2012年全国优秀大学生夏令营 ——入选营员签到须知', 'cn', 0, 11, '', '', '<p>\n	<strong>签到时间：</strong>7月5日早7：30\n</p>\n<p>\n	<br />\n<strong>签到地点：</strong>上海市杨浦区国顺路670号,复旦大学管理学院李达三楼2楼报告厅\n</p>\n<p>\n	<br />\n<strong>必须携带的材料清单及物品：</strong><br />\n1、身份证及复印件<br />\n2、学生证原件及复印件<br />\n3、笔记本电脑（报考硕博连读项目）\n</p>\n<p>\n	<br />\n<strong>注意事项：</strong><br />\n1、7月4日下午15：00后，外埠高校营员即可直接到达指定酒店（请严格按照安排入住，切勿自行更换，否则后果自负）；上海高校营员不提供住宿。<br />\n汉庭快捷酒店：上海市杨浦区松花江路2628号（近邯郸路）　　电话：021-61434888<br />\n2、所有营员请在<strong> 7月5日早7：30 </strong>前直接到达开营式现场签到（地址：复旦大学管理学院李达三楼2楼报告厅），现场将有工作人员指引。<br />\n3、外校推免生复试名单将在营员到达后公布。<br />\n4、报销注意事项：<br />\n外埠高校营员：请大家保存好往返火车票票根（若乘坐飞机，请将往返机票及登机牌保存完好），以便报销所用（请在车票背后写上姓名加以区分）。<strong><br />\n特别提醒：（1）请将票根于2012年7月27日（以寄达日期为准）前寄至以下地址，过期不予以报销；（2）邮政汇款单请于7月5日学术讲座后交至签到台处，以便报销后汇款。</strong> \n</p>\n<p>\n	<br />\n火车票票根邮寄地址：上海市杨浦区国顺路670号复旦大学管理学院教学管理办公室李达三楼201室（邮编：200433）\n</p>', '', '', '', '', '', '2012年全国优秀大学生夏令营 ——入选营员签到须知', 1351133079, 0, 1, '', 0, '', '2012 national outstanding college students summer camp -- selected campers check-in notes', '', '<div id="trans-result-content" lang="EN-US">\n	<p>\n		<span class="">Sign in time</span><span>:</span><span> as early as July 5th</span><span> 7:30</span>\n	</p>\n	<p>\n		<span class="">Sign in</span><span class=""> place: Shanghai</span><span class=""> Yangpu District</span><span> country</span><span> road</span><span> No. 670</span><span>,</span><span class=""> the school of management of Fudan University</span><span> Li Da</span><span> hall</span><span> on the third floor of</span><span> 2</span>\n	</p>\n	<p>\n		<span class="">Must carry</span><span> the bill of material and</span><span> goods</span><span>:</span>\n	</p>\n	<p>\n		<span>1</span><span>,</span><span> ID and photocopy</span>\n	</p>\n	<p>\n		<span>2</span><span>,</span><span class=""> student id</span><span> original and photocopy</span>\n	</p>\n	<p>\n		<span>3</span><span>,</span><span class=""> notebook</span><span> computer</span><span> (RNs</span><span class=""> Shuoboliandu</s