(107, 'DDIM项目中意两国79名新生入学', 'cn', 0, 6, '', '', '<p style="text-align:left;">\n	9月19日，复旦-博科尼/路易斯国际商务硕士项目（DDIM项目）2011级开学典礼在我院举行，来自中意两国79名新生由此正式加入DDIM项目的大家庭，成为自2006年项目创立以来的第六届学生。殷志文副院长主持了本次活动。\n</p>\n<p>\n	<br />\n</p>\n<p style="text-align:center;">\n	<img alt="DDIM" src="http://www.fdsm.fudan.edu.cn/UserWebEditorUploadImage/J2nlSDxtSEk/201109220010.jpg" height="215" width="500" /> \n</p>\n<p style="text-align:center;">\n	DDIM项目2011级开学典礼师生合影\n</p>\n<p style="text-align:center;">\n	<br />\n</p>\n<p>\n	我院吕长江副院长热情洋溢的发言拉开了开学典礼的序幕。他在回顾了DDIM项目6年来发展的基础上指出：DDIM项目不仅为社会培养了一批具有全球视野的优秀管理型人才，同时也成为两国教育、文化交流的纽带，他衷心地期望学生们可以充分利用两国高校的优势资源，在DDIM项目这个独特的平台上完成自己人生的飞跃。\n</p>\n<p>\n	<br />\n</p>\n<p style="text-align:center;">\n	<img alt="ddim" src="http://www.fdsm.fudan.edu.cn/UserWebEditorUploadImage/J2nlSDxtSEk/201109220011.jpg" height="335" width="500" /> \n</p>\n<p style="text-align:center;">\n	吕长江副院长在开学典礼上致辞\n</p>\n<p style="text-align:center;">\n	<br />\n</p>\n<p>\n	随后，Luiss大学和Bocconi大学的两位项目总监Giovanni Fiori教授、Roberto Dona教授以及意大利驻沪领事馆总领事Vincenzo De Luca先生相继发言。他们从项目发展、两国经济文化联系等角度，指出中意两国的商贸往来和双边文化交流为学生们提供了广阔的舞台，并对项目新生寄予期望，希望他们能够为中意两国未来的交流、合作与发展做出贡献。&nbsp;\n</p>\n<p style="text-align:center;">\n	<img alt="ddim" src="http://www.fdsm.fudan.edu.cn/UserWebEditorUploadImage/J2nlSDxtSEk/201109220012.jpg" height="352" width="500" /> \n</p>\n<p align="center">\n	(上排左起) Luiss大学项目总监Giovanni Fiori教授、Bocconi大学项目总监Roberto Dona教授、意大利驻沪领事馆总领事Vincenzo De Luca先生,(下排左起) Bocconi大学的校友Andrea Goldstein先生、Luiss大学的校友Edoardo Vittucci先生先后在典礼中发言　\n</p>\n<p align="center">\n	<br />\n</p>\n<p>\n	最后，殷志文院长在总结发言中肯定了项目在培养学生的过程中取得的瞩目成绩，并希望新同学们能够珍惜在中国和意大利的学习、生活经历，与项目携手发展、共同进步。最后，所有师生在史带楼前集体合影留念，在灿烂的微笑中，同学们承载着希望走向明天。\n</p>\n<p>\n	<br />\n</p>\n<p align="right">\n	教学管理办公室\n</p>\n<p align="right">\n	2011年9月22日\n</p>', '', '', '', '', '/201210/25/110315d1ndphb2zegtof1o.jpg', '9月19日，复旦-博科尼/路易斯国际商务硕士项目（DDIM项目）2011级开学典礼在我院举行，来自中意两国79名新生由此正式加入DDIM项目的大家庭，成为自2006年项目创立以来的第六届学生。殷志文副院长主持了本次活动。我院吕长江副院长热情洋溢的发言拉开了开学典礼的序幕。他在回顾了DDIM项目6年来发展的基础上指出：DDIM项目不仅为社会培养了一批具有全球视野的优秀管理型人才，同时也成为两国教育、', 1323070311, 0, 1, '', 3, 'September 20, 2011', 'The DDIM project of China and the 79 freshmen', 'On September 19, the Fudan-Bocconi/Luiss DDIM (Double Degree in International Management) Programme 2011 Class Opening Ceremony was held in FDSM. Thus, seventy-nine new students from China and Italy formally entered the big “family” of DDIM programme and became the sixth session of students since this programme was founded in 2006. Associate Dean Yin Zhiwen presided this event. ', '<p style="text-align:left;">\n	<br />\n</p>\n<div id="trans-result-content" lang="EN-US">\n	<p>\n		<span class="">\n		<p style="margin-left:0cm;text-indent:24.0pt;background:white;">\n			<span style="font-size:9.0pt;font-family:&quot;color:#3B3B3B;">On September 19, the Fudan-Bocconi/Luiss DDIM (Double Degree in\nInternational Management) Programme 2011 Class Opening Ceremony was held in\nFDSM. Thus, seventy-nine new students from China and Italy formally entered the\nbig “family” of DDIM programme and became the sixth session of students since\nthis programme was founded in 2006. Associate Dean Yin Zhiwen presided this\nevent.</span><span style="font-size:9.0pt;font-family:&quot;color:#3B3B3B;"> </span>\n		</p>\n</span><span class=""></span> \n	</p>\n</div>\n<p>\n	<br />\n</p>\n<p>\n	<br />\n</p>\n<p style="text-align:center;">\n	<img alt="DDIM" src="http://www.fdsm.fudan.edu.cn/UserWebEditorUploadImage/J2nlSDxtSEk/201109220010.jpg" height="215" width="500" /> \n</p>\n<p style="text-align:center;">\n	<p style="margin-left:0cm;text-align:center;text-indent:24.0pt;background:white;" align="center">\n		<span style="font-size:9.0pt;font-family:&quot;color:#3B3B3B;">Group Photo of Faculty and Students of DDIM Programme 2011 Class\nOpening Ceremony</span><span style="font-size:9.0pt;font-family:&quot;color:#3B3B3B;"></span>\n	</p>\n</p>\n<div id="trans-result-content" lang="EN-US">\n	<p>\n		<span class=""></span><span></span><span></span><span class=""></span> \n	</p>\n</div>\n<p>\n	<br />\n</p>\n<p style="text-align:center;">\n	<br />\n</p>\n<p>\n	<br />\n</p>\n<div id="trans-result-content" lang="EN-US">\n	<p>\n		<span class="">\n		<p style="margin-left:0cm;text-align:left;text-indent:24.0pt;background:white;" align="left">\n			<span style="font-size:9.0pt;font-family:&quot;color:#3B3B3B;">Accompanied by the ardent speech Lv Changjiang, Associate Dean\nof FDSM, the opening ceremony began. Mr. Lv reviewed the six-year development\nof DDIM programme and pointed out that the DDIM programme had not only trained\na group of outstanding management talents with international vision, but also\nbecome the link of educational and cultural exchange between China and Italy.\nHe heartily expected that students would be able to make full use of the advantageous\nresources of the colleges and universities of the two countries, and achieve\ntheir life leaps on this unique platform of DDIM programme.</span><span style="font-size:9.0pt;font-family:&quot;color:#3B3B3B;"></span>\n		</p>\n</span>\n	</p>\n</div>\n<p>\n	<br />\n</p>\n<p>\n	<br />\n</p>\n<p style="text-align:center;">\n	<img alt="ddim" src="http://www.fdsm.fudan.edu.cn/UserWebEditorUploadImage/J2nlSDxtSEk/201109220011.jpg" height="335" width="500" /> \n</p>\n<p style="text-align:center;">\n	<span style="font-size:9.0pt;font-family:&quot;color:#3B3B3B;">Associate Dean Lv\nChangjiang is making a speech at the opening ceremony</span>\n</p>\n<p style="text-align:center;">\n	<br />\n</p>\n<p>\n	<br />\n</p>\n<div id="trans-result-content" lang="EN-US">\n	<p>\n		<span class="">\n		<p style="margin-left:0cm;text-align:left;text-indent:24.0pt;background:white;" align="left">\n			<span style="font-size:9.0pt;font-family:&quot;color:#3B3B3B;">Subsequently, the two programme directors of Luiss University and\nBocconi University, Professor Giovanni Fiori and Professor Roberto Dona, as\nwell as Mr. Vincenzo De Luca, Consulate-general of Italy in Shanghai, addressed\none after another. From the standpoints of programme development as well as\neconomic and cultural ties between China and Italy, etc., they pointed out that\nthe trade and cultural exchanges between the two countries provided a broad\nstage for students and that they expected the new students of this programme to\nbe able to contribute to the future exchange, cooperation and development of\nthe two countries.</span><span style="font-size:9.0pt;font-family:&quot;color:#3B3B3B;"></span>\n		</p>\n</span><span class=""></span> \n	</p>\n</div>\n<p>\n	<br />\n</p>\n<p style="text-align:center;">\n	<img alt="ddim" src="http://www.fdsm.fudan.edu.cn/UserWebEditorUploadImage/J2nlSDxtSEk/201109220012.jpg" height="352" width="500" /> \n</p>\n<p align="center">\n	<br />\n</p>\n<div id="trans-result-content" lang="EN-US">\n	<p>\n		<span class="">(</span><span class=""> last</span><span class=""> row</span><span> from left</span><span> )</span><span> Luiss</span><span> university</span><span> project director</span><span> Giovanni</span><span> Fiori</span><span>,</span><span class=""> Professor</span><span class="highlight"> Bocconi</span><span class=""> university</span><span> project director</span><span> Roberto</span><span> Dona</span><span> Professor</span><span>,</span><span> Italy consulate</span><span class=""> Consulate General Vincenzo</span><span> De</span><span> Luca</span><span>,</span><span> (</span><span> lower</span><span> left)</span><span> Bocconi</span><span> University</span><span> Alumni</span><span class=""> Andrea</span><span class=""> Goldstein</span><span>,</span><span> Mr.</span><span> Luiss</span><span> university</span><span> school</span><span> friend</span><span> Edoardo</span><span> Mr. Vittucci</span><span> in</span><span> ceremony</span><span class=""> speech</span> \n	</p>\n</div>\n<p>\n	<br />\n</p>\n<p align="center">\n	<br />\n</p>\n<p>\n	<br />\n</p>\n<div id="trans-result-content" lang="EN-US">\n	<p>\n		<span class="">\n		<p style="margin-left:0cm;text-align:center;text-indent:24.0pt;background:white;" align="center">\n			<span style="font-size:9.0pt;font-family:&quot;color:#3B3B3B;">(from the upper left) Professor Giovanni Fiori, Programme\nDirector of Luiss University, Professor Roberto Dona, Programme Director of\nBocconi University, and Mr. Vincenzo De Luca, Consulate-general of Italy in\nShanghai; (from the lower left) Mr. Andrea Goldstein, an alumnus of Bocconi\nUniversity, and Mr. Edoardo Vittucci, an alumnus of Luiss University, are\naddressing successively at the ceremony.</span><span style="font-size:9.0pt;font-family:&quot;color:#3B3B3B;"></span>\n		</p>\n</span>\n	</p>\n</div>\n<p>\n	<p style="margin-left:0cm;text-align:left;text-indent:24.0pt;background:white;" align="left">\n		<span style="font-size:9.0pt;font-family:&quot;color:#3B3B3B;">In the summarized speech, Associate Dean Yin Zhiwen affirmed the\nnoticeable achievements of this programme in the process of student\ncultivation, and hoped that the new students would cherish their school life\nboth in China and in Italy, and make common development and progress together\nwith this programme. Finally, all the faculty and students posed for a group\nphoto in front of the Starr Building. With a bright smile on face, the students\nadvanced towards the future with hopes.</span><span style="font-size:9.0pt;font-family:&quot;color:#3B3B3B;"> </span>\n	</p>\n</p>\n<p>\n	<br />\n</p>\n<p align="right">\n	<span style="font-size:9.0pt;font-family:&quot;color:#3B3B3B;">Teaching Management Office</span><span style="font-size:9.0pt;font-family:&quot;color:#3B3B3B;"> </span>\n</p>\n<div id="trans-result-content" lang="EN-US">\n	<p>\n		<span class=""></span><span class=""></span> \n	</p>\n	<p>\n		<span class="">September 22, 2011</span> \n	</p>\n</div>\n<p>\n	<br />\n</p>\n<p align="right">\n	<br />\n</p>\n<br />'),
(138, 'Li Deyuan 黎德元', 'cn', 0, 31, '', '', '<div align="center">\r\n	<p>\r\n		<img height="300" alt="" src="/uploads/image/20121018/20121018151158_17984.jpg" width="200" /> \r\n	</p>\r\n	<p align="left">\r\n		&nbsp; Deyuan Li is an associate professor of statistics at School of Management, Fudan University (FDSM). He graduated from School of Mathematical Science, Peking University on 1997 and 2000, and got his bachelor and master degree, respectively. After finishing his Ph.D. study and obtaining his doctoral degree in 2004 at School of Economics, Erasmus University of Rotterdam (the Netherlands), Prof. Li moved to University of Bern (Switzerland) and worked as a post-doctoral and research assistant at Department of Statistics. Then he joined in FDSM in 2008. Prof. Li’s research is on statistics of extremes, and he has already published several papers on the top journals such as Annals of Statistics, Journal of American Statistical Association, Econometric Theory and etc. Prof. Li had 2 grants from NNSFC and 1 grant from SEM, and he visited several times CUHK, GIT, NCSU, and MIT Sloan.\r\n	</p>\r\n</div>', '', '', '', '', '/201210/18/151331z1mis1knldg9jqz1.jpg', 'Deyuan Li is an associate professor of statistics at School of Management, Fudan University (FDSM). He graduated from School of Mathematical Science, Peking University on 1997 and 2000, and got his ba', 1350537500, 0, 1, '', 0, '', 'Li Deyuan', 'Deyuan Li is an associate professor of statistics at School of Management, Fudan University (FDSM). He graduated from School of Mathematical Science, Peking University on 1997 and 2000, and got his ba', '<div align="center">\r\n	<p>\r\n		<img height="300" alt="" src="/uploads/image/20121018/20121018151158_17984.jpg" width="200" /> \r\n	</p>\r\n	<p align="left">\r\n		&nbsp; Deyuan Li is an associate professor of statistics at School of Management, Fudan University (FDSM). He graduated from School of Mathematical Science, Peking University on 1997 and 2000, and got his bachelor and master degree, respectively. After finishing his Ph.D. study and obtaining his doctoral degree in 2004 at School of Economics, Erasmus University of Rotterdam (the Netherlands), Prof. Li moved to University of Bern (Switzerland) and worked as a post-doctoral and research assistant at Department of Statistics. Then he joined in FDSM in 2008. Prof. Li’s research is on statistics of extremes, and he has already published several papers on the top journals such as Annals of Statistics, Journal of American Statistical Association, Econometric Theory and etc. Prof. Li had 2 grants from NNSFC and 1 grant from SEM, and he visited several times CUHK, GIT, NCSU, and MIT Sloan.\r\n	</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<br />');
