(155, '复旦-博科尼/路易斯管理学双硕士学位项目（DDIM）首届学生完成毕业答辩', 'cn', 0, 6, '', '', '<p>\n	&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 复旦-博科尼/路易斯管理学双硕士学位项目（DDIM）首届30名中国学生，在经历了两年的学习生活后，于2008年7月23日至7月28日，分别在意大利博科尼大学和路易斯大学进行了硕士论文答辩。管理学院党委书记黄丽华教授代表学校赴意大利，全程参加了这30名同学的论文答辩。30名同学的论文得到了众多评委的肯定，均顺利通过答辩。其中更有一名同学在论文陈述和问答环节发挥出色，其论文质量得到了答辩委员会成员的一致好评，获得了满分的好成绩。至此，复旦-博科尼/路易斯管理学双硕士学位项目（DDIM）第一届学生顺利完成了培养计划所规定的所有课程，正式从两所意大利大学毕业，得到两所大学颁发的硕士学位证书。之后他们将回国完成复旦大学的所有毕业流程，在得到学校学位委员会批准后，将获得复旦大学研究生毕业证书和硕士学位证书。\n</p>\n<p>\n	&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 该项目第二届29位中国学生和25名意大利学生完成了他们在复旦一年的学习后，今年九月将启程前往意大利开始新学期的学习。与此同时，第三届学生将进入复旦大学管理学院，开始他们在复旦新的学习生活，第三届包括31名中国学生和33名意大利学生，是该项目创立以来规模最大的一批学生。\n</p>', '', '', '', '', '/201210/30/094638rmadjd21afoashuq.jpg', '复旦-博科尼/路易斯管理学双硕士学位项目（DDIM）首届30名中国学生，在经历了两年的学习生活后，于2008年7月23日至7月28日，分别在意大利博科尼大学和路易斯大学进行了硕士论文答辩。', 1351561616, 0, 1, '', 1, '2008-09-01', 'The First Session of Fudan-Bocconi/Luiss DDIM Programme Students Complete Graduation Thesis Defense', 'After their two-year study, the 30 Chinese students of the first session of Fudan-Bocconi/Luiss DDIM programme participated in the master thesis defense in Bocconi University and Luiss University in Italy respectively on July 23-28, 2008. On behalf of Fudan University, Professor Huang Lihua, Secretary of the Party Committee of School of Management, went to Italy and attended the whole thesis defense of the 30 students. These theses got the affirmation of many judges and the students passed the t', '<div id="trans-result-content" lang="EN-US">\n	<p>\n		<span class="">\n		<p style="margin-left:0cm;text-indent:24.0pt;background:white;">\n			<span style="font-size:9.0pt;font-family:&quot;color:#3B3B3B;">After their two-year study, the 30 Chinese students of the first\nsession of Fudan-Bocconi/Luiss DDIM programme participated in the master thesis\ndefense in Bocconi University and Luiss University in Italy respectively on\nJuly 23-28, 2008. On behalf of Fudan University, Professor Huang Lihua,\nSecretary of the Party Committee of School of Management, went to Italy and\nattended the whole thesis defense of the 30 students. These theses got the\naffirmation of many judges and the students passed the thesis defense\nsuccessfully. One student among them got full marks because he did well in the\nthesis statement and QAQs and his thesis won him praise from all members of the\nDefense Committee. So far, the students of the first session of\nFudan-Bocconi/Luiss DDIM programme smoothly completed all the courses as\nstipulated by the training programme, formally graduated from the two Italian\nuniversities and received their certificates of master’s degree. Later, they\nwould return home to complete all the graduation processes of Fudan University;\nthey would gain the graduation certificates of postgraduate students and\ncertificates of master’s degree of Fudan University upon approval of the\nacademic degree evaluation of the university.</span><span style="font-size:9.0pt;font-family:&quot;color:#3B3B3B;"></span>\n		</p>\n</span>\n	</p>\n</div>\n<p style="margin-left:0cm;text-indent:24.0pt;background:white;">\n	<span style="font-size:9.0pt;font-family:&quot;color:#3B3B3B;">After their one-year study in Fudan University, the 29 Chinese\nstudents and 25 Italian students of the second session of this programme will\ngo to Italy to begin the study of a new term in September 2008. Meanwhile, the\nstudents of the third session will enter FDSM to begin their new school life\nthere. The third session, which will include 31 Chinese students and 33 Italian\nstudents, will see the most students since this programme was founded.</span><span style="font-size:9.0pt;font-family:&quot;color:#3B3B3B;"></span>\n</p>\n<br />'),
(154, '复旦管院2012级DDIM学员“破冰”活动在沪举行', 'cn', 0, 6, '', '', '<p>\n	<span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 复旦大学管理学院<span lang="EN-US">2012</span>级<span lang="EN-US">DDIM</span>（国际商务双硕士项目）学员“破冰”活动于上周五（<st1:chsdate xmlns:st1="http://unknownprefix/st1" isrocdate="False" islunardate="False" day="21" month="9" year="2012" st="on"><span lang="EN-US">9</span>月<span lang="EN-US">21</span>日</st1:chsdate>）在上海东方绿舟隆重举行。<span lang="EN-US">2012</span>级<span lang="EN-US">DDIM</span>项目意大利学员与复旦大学的同学们一起参加本次“破冰”活动。</span> \n</p>\n<p>\n	<span lang="EN-US">&nbsp;</span> \n</p>\n<div align="center">\n	<img alt="" src="http://www.fdsm.fudan.edu.cn/UserWebEditorUploadImage/YU2+rvN0IHs/DDIM破冰.png" border="0" height="400" hspace="0" width="550" /> \n</div>\n<p>\n	<br />\n</p>\n<p>\n	<span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;据悉，本次活动由管理学院教学管理办公室老师带队，前往东方绿舟进行各项活动。在一天时间里分别进行了“双人默契运物”、“友谊报纸”、“传递纸巾”、“携手划龙舟”、“翻山越岭”等项目。旨在通过丰富多彩的文娱活动，使两国学生进一步加深了解与信任，充分搭建中意两国大学生的友谊之桥，续写复旦管理学院学子们兼济天下的豪情与气概。</span> \n</p>\n<p>\n	<span lang="EN-US">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;2012</span><span>级<span lang="EN-US">DDIM</span>项目中国研究生李雨虹同学介绍道，本次“破冰”活动是开学以来的第二次。虽然游戏项目与竞赛类型不同，但都充分考验与锻造了中意两国大学生们坚忍不拔的意志品质：“无论遇到什么困难，大家都手与手紧紧相连，心与心紧紧相依，齐心协力共度难关。”本次<span lang="EN-US">DDIM</span>项目意大利研究生<span lang="EN-US">Luca</span>也表示，尽管这是他首次来华深造，但在复旦大学师生们热情的帮助与关怀下，他已将复旦当作他的第二个家。</span> \n</p>\n<div>\n	<span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;下午<span lang="EN-US">6</span>时许，复旦管理学院<span lang="EN-US">2012</span>级<span lang="EN-US">DDIM</span>项目的两国大学生们经过考验与合作，带着满身疲惫与收获坐上回校客车。本次“破冰”活动在第一次“破冰”活动基础上进行了大胆创新与突破，增加了挑战性与趣味性，更加考验同学间面对困难与挑战时冷静思考与合作协同能力。复旦管理学院<span lang="EN-US">DDIM</span>项目中意两国大学生之间的文化交流活动和谐有序进行，为中意人民友谊做出自己微薄的贡献。</span> \n</div>', '', '', '', '', '/201210/30/094322vah99u9ipmeipm4d.jpg', ' 复旦大学管理学院2012级DDIM（国际商务双硕士项目）学员“破冰”活动于上周五（9月21日）在上海东方绿舟隆重举行。2012级DDIM项目意大利学员与复旦大学的同学们一起参加本次“破冰”活动。', 1351561410, 0, 1, '', 5, 'October 2, 2012', 'The ”Icebreaking” Activity of DDIM 2012 Class of FDSM Held in Shanghai', 'The “Icebreaking” activity of DDIM (Double Degree in International Management) 2012 Class of FDSM was grandly held at the Oriental Land, Shanghai, last Friday (September 21). Italian trainees and students of Fudan University of DDIM 2012 Class participated in this activity together.', '<p>\n	<span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span>\n</p>\n<div id="trans-result-content" lang="EN-US">\n	<p>\n		<span class="">\n		<p style="margin-left:0cm;text-indent:24.0pt;background:white;">\n			<span style="font-size:9.0pt;font-family:&quot;color:#3B3B3B;">The “Icebreaking” activity of DDIM (Double Degree in\nInternational Management) 2012 Class of FDSM was grandly held at the Oriental\nLand, Shanghai, last Friday (September 21). Italian trainees and students of\nFudan University of DDIM 2012 Class participated in this activity together.</span><span style="font-size:9.0pt;font-family:&quot;color:#3B3B3B;"></span>\n		</p>\n</span><span class=""></span> \n	</p>\n</div>\n<p>\n	<br />\n</p>\n<p>\n	<span lang="EN-US">&nbsp;</span> \n</p>\n<div align="center">\n	<img alt="" src="http://www.fdsm.fudan.edu.cn/UserWebEditorUploadImage/YU2+rvN0IHs/DDIM破冰.png" border="0" height="400" hspace="0" width="550" /> \n</div>\n<p>\n	<br />\n</p>\n<p>\n	<span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span>\n</p>\n<div id="trans-result-content" lang="EN-US">\n	<p>\n		<span class="">\n		<p style="margin-left:0cm;text-indent:24.0pt;background:white;">\n			<span style="font-size:9.0pt;font-family:&quot;color:#3B3B3B;">It is known that the teachers of the teaching management office\nof School of Management led trainees and students to Oriental Land to carry out\nactivities. On a day, they respectively finished conducting such programmes as\n“Two Persons Carry Articles in Perfect Unison”, “Friendship Newspaper”, “Pass\non Paper Towel”, “Row Dragon Boats Hand in Hand” and “Climb Mountains”. These\nrecreational activities aimed to further deepen the understanding and trust\nbetween students of China and Italy, to fully set up the friendship bridge\nbetween college students of the two countries, and to show the passion and\nspirit of caring about the whole society by the students of School of\nManagement.</span>\n		</p>\n		<p style="margin-left:0cm;text-indent:24.0pt;background:white;">\n			<p style="margin-left:0cm;text-indent:24.0pt;background:white;">\n				<span style="font-size:9.0pt;font-family:&quot;color:#3B3B3B;">Li Yuhong, a Chinese postgraduate of DDIM 2012 Class said that\nthis is the second “Icebreaking” activity since this term began. Although both\nactivities have different game programmes and contest types, they have both\nfully tested and forged the <span><span style="color:#3B3B3B;">fortitudinous</span></span> will and quality of college\nstudents of China and Italy. “Whatever difficulties we met with, we will always\npull together to overcome them,” said Li. Luca, an Italian postgraduate of this\nDDIM also indicated that despite his first further education in China, he had\ntaken Fudan as his second family with the warm help and care of teachers and\nstudents of Fudan University.</span><span style="font-size:9.0pt;font-family:&quot;color:#3B3B3B;"></span>\n			</p>\n			<p style="text-indent:13.5pt;background:white;">\n				<span style="font-size:9.0pt;font-family:&quot;color:#3B3B3B;">At 6:00 p.m., after the test and cooperation, the fatigued\ncollege students of 2012 Class DDIM program of FDSM started to take buses to\nreturn with lots of gains. On the basis of the first “Icebreaking” activity,\nthis activity made bold innovation and breakthroughs with increased challenges\nand enjoyment to test the calm thought and cooperative abilities of the\nstudents in the face of difficulties and challenges. The activity of DDIM\nprogramme of FDSM between college students of China and Italy was carried out\nboth harmoniously and orderly, thus making contribution to the friendship of\nthe two countries’ people.</span><span style="font-size:9.0pt;font-family:&quot;color:#3B3B3B;"></span>\n			</p>\n			<p style="text-indent:13.5pt;background:white;">\n				<span style="font-size:9.0pt;font-family:&quot;color:#3B3B3B;"></span>\n			</p>\n<br />\n<span style="font-size:9.0pt;font-family:&quot;color:#3B3B3B;"></span><span style="font-size:9.0pt;font-family:&quot;color:#3B3B3B;"></span>\n		</p>\n</span>\n	</p>\n</div>\n<br />'),
(157, 'DDIM项目2010级开学典礼在世博园意大利馆举行', 'cn', 0, 6, '', '', '<p>\n	&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 2010年9月11日，<span>复旦—博科尼路易斯管理学双硕士学位项目（</span>DDIM项目）2010级开学典礼在世博园区意大利馆举行。意大利馆馆长Beniamino Quintieri教授为开学典礼致欢迎辞。意大利驻沪领馆文化处官员Giorgio Casacchia教授，复旦大学管理学院副院长殷志文教授，Luiss大学经济学院院长Giorgior Di Giorgio教授，以及Bocconi大学对外事务院长Fulvio Ortu教授相继发言，从不同角度对项目新生寄予期望，希望学生能够为中意两国文化交流和商贸往来做出贡献。\n</p>\n<p style="text-align:center;">\n	<img alt="" src="http://www.fdsm.fudan.edu.cn/UserWebEditorUploadImage/Bn1XisBTnM/100903/DDIM.jpg" height="171" width="500" /> \n</p>\n<p>\n	&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 来自复旦、博科尼、路易斯三校的校友代表也分别发言，肯定了项目对学生事业发展起到的积极作用，并希望新同学们能够珍惜在中国和意大利的生活学习经历，为项目发展添砖加瓦。\n</p>', '', '', '', '', '/201210/31/142350jzqsvp3qykplkrc5.jpg', '2010年9月11日，复旦—博科尼路易斯管理学双硕士学位项目（DDIM项目）2010级开学典礼在世博园区意大利馆举行。', 1351664642, 0, 1, '', 2, 'September 16, 2010', 'DDIM Programme 2010 Class Opening Ceremony Held in the Italian Pavilion in World Expo Park', 'On September 11, 2010, the Fudan-Bocconi/Luiss DDIM (Double Degree in International Management) Programme 2011 Class Opening Ceremony was held in the Italian Pavilion in World Expo Park. Professor Beniamino Quintieri, Italian Pavillion Director, delievered a speech to welcome the opening ceremony. Professor Giorgio Casacchia, an official of the cultural section of Consulate-general of Italy in Shanghai, Professor Yin Zhiwen, Associate Dean of School of Management, Fudan University, Professor Gio', '<div id="trans-result-content" lang="EN-US">\n	<p>\n		<span class="">\n		<p style="margin-left:0cm;text-indent:24.0pt;background:white;">\n			<span style="font-size:9.0pt;font-family:&quot;color:#3B3B3B;">On September 11, 2010, the Fudan-Bocconi/Luiss DDIM (Double\nDegree in International Management) Programme 2011 Class Opening Ceremony was\nheld in the Italian Pavilion in World Expo Park. Professor Beniamino Quintieri,\nItalian Pavillion Director, delievered a speech to welcome the opening\nceremony. Professor Giorgio Casacchia, an official of the cultural section of\nConsulate-general of Italy in Shanghai, Professor Yin Zhiwen, Associate Dean of\nSchool of Management, Fudan University, Professor Giorgior Di Giorgio, Dean of School\nof Economics of Luiss University, and Professor Fulvio Ortu, Dean of Foreign\nAffairs of Bocconi University, made a speech one after another, expressing\ntheir expectations of new students of the programme, and hoping that they would\nbe able to contribute to the cultural exchange and trade between China and\nItaly.</span><span style="font-size:9.0pt;font-family:&quot;color:#3B3B3B;"></span>\n		</p>\n</span><span class=""></span> \n	</p>\n</div>\n<p style="text-align:center;">\n	<img alt="" src="http://www.fdsm.fudan.edu.cn/UserWebEditorUploadImage/Bn1XisBTnM/100903/DDIM.jpg" height="171" width="500" /> \n</p>\n<p>\n	&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\n</p>\n<div id="trans-result-content" lang="EN-US">\n	<p>\n		<span class="">\n		<p style="margin-left:0cm;text-align:left;text-indent:24.0pt;background:white;" align="left">\n			<span style="font-size:9.0pt;font-family:&quot;color:#3B3B3B;">Alumnus representatives from Fudan University, Bocconi\nUniversity and Luiss University also addressed respectively. They affirmed that\nthis programme had played an active role in developing the careers of students,\nand expected that new students would be able to value their school life in\nChina and Italy to promote the programme development.</span><span style="font-size:9.0pt;font-family:&quot;color:#3B3B3B;"></span>\n		</p>\n</span>\n	</p>\n</div>\n<br />'),
