(162, 'Giovanni Fiori', 'cn', 0, 31, '', '', '<span><a href="http://docenti.luiss.it/fiori/files/2007/12/prof-2.jpg"><span style="color:blue;text-decoration:none;"></span></a></span> \n<p style="text-align:justify;" align="center">\n	<b>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <img alt="" src="/uploads/image/20121107/20121107081216_84100.jpg" height="300" width="227" /></b> \n</p>\n<p style="text-align:justify;" align="center">\n	<b><span style="font-size:14pt;font-family:‘Calibri‘,‘sans-serif‘;"></span></b>&nbsp;<b><span style="font-size:12px;font-family:‘Calibri‘,‘sans-serif‘;">Giovanni Fiori </span></b><span style="font-size:12px;background:white;font-family:‘Calibri‘,‘sans-serif‘;">is Full Professor of Business Administration since 2000 september the 15th at “LUISS - Guido Carli” University of Rome. He is also Member of Evaluation Committee of “LUISS - Guido Carli” University, Professor of Accounting and M&amp;A of Master in Business Administration at LUISS- Management School since 1991, Member of Italian Accounting Association since 1993, Member of European Accounting Association since 1994 and Member of “Società Italiana di Storia della Ragioneria” since 1995. </span><span style="font-size:12px;background:white;font-family:‘Calibri‘,‘sans-serif‘;">Giovanni Fiori is also a C.P.A. (Dottore Commercialista) in Rome since 1988, a Certified Auditor (Revisore dei Conti). </span><span style="font-size:12pt;background:white;font-family:‘Calibri‘,‘sans-serif‘;"><span style="font-size:12px;">He is the Vice President of</span><span style="font-size:12px;">&nbsp; </span><span style="font-size:12px;">“Istituto Poligrafico e Zecca dello Stato S.p.A” and covers the postion of Extraordinary Commissioner of Ilva Pali Dalmine S.p.A. in Extraordinary Admistration Procedure (law Prodi-bis), of Ilva Pali Dalmine design Community S.r.l. and of Sidercomit Centro Meridionale S.r.l. and Extraordinary Commissioner of Cesame S.p.A. in Extraordinary Admistration Procedure (law Prodi-bis). He is also Member of Board of Directors of “Istituto dell’Enciclopedia Italiana Treccani Spa” and Member of Board of Directors of “Ned Community” (indipendent directors association of listed companies). He is consultant in financial reporting for Anas SpA and for reporting for “Acquirente Unico SpA” since 2005. He holds a Degree in Economics from“LUISS - Guido Carli” University of Rome in 1984, with 110/110 cum laude.</span></span> \n</p>\n<p style="text-align:justify;">\n	<span style="font-size:12px;background:white;font-family:‘Calibri‘,‘sans-serif‘;">He held a course of “Accounting” at the School of Management of Fudan University.</span> \n</p>', '', '', '', '', '/201211/07/081242l1ygjdzjgxrb7epb.jpg', 'Giovanni Fiori is Full Professor of Business Administration since 2000 september the 15th at “LUISS - Guido Carli” University of Rome. He is also Member of Evaluation Committee of “LUISS - Guido Carli', 1352247186, 0, 1, '', 0, '', 'Giovanni Fiori', 'Giovanni Fiori is Full Professor of Business Administration since 2000 september the 15th at “LUISS - Guido Carli” University of Rome. He is also Member of Evaluation Committee of “LUISS - Guido Carli', '<span><a href="http://docenti.luiss.it/fiori/files/2007/12/prof-2.jpg"><span style="color:blue;text-decoration:none;"></span></a></span> \n<p style="text-align:justify;" align="center">\n	<b>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <img alt="" src="/uploads/image/20121107/20121107081216_84100.jpg" height="300" width="227" /></b> \n</p>\n<p style="text-